WEBVTT

00:00:55.977 --> 00:01:00.008
the first primitive cells
started to evolve on this planet.

00:01:00.529 --> 00:01:05.743
It took spiders 430 million years
to become what they are now:

00:01:05.767 --> 00:01:07.919
one of the most versatile,

00:01:07.943 --> 00:01:09.906
one of the most diverse

00:01:09.930 --> 00:01:14.724
and one of the most evolved groups --

00:01:14.748 --> 00:01:15.843
(Laughter)

00:01:15.867 --> 00:01:18.627
of predators to ever walk this earth.

00:01:19.070 --> 00:01:21.850
It's actually quite sporty
to give a speech

00:01:21.874 --> 00:01:23.922
while wrangling a tarantula,
I have to say.

00:01:23.946 --> 00:01:28.130
(Laughter)

00:01:28.154 --> 00:01:31.310
So, we shouldn't forget that Sophie --